---
preview: Java install linux
title: Java Linux
tags: Java
author: rrLero
date: 2018-12-20 09:22:00
---
1. Install Java folder to JAVA_HOME `echo $JAVA_HOME`
2. In terminal `export PATH=$PWD/MY_JDK_FOLDER/bin:$PATH`
3. `which java` - will show run-file
4. In Idea find icon "Project Structure" (ctrl + alt + shift + s), and choose correct java
5. Refresh Gradle